    <directions>
      <step>
	<para>Clean chokes, including lots of leaves</para>
      </step>
      <step>
	<para>Skin the stem and cut off the top</para>
      </step>
      <step>
	<para>Put artichikes in a shallow pan with water, oil, salt and pepper, mint.</para>
      </step>
      <step>
	<para>Cook, covered, until soft (20-30 minutes)</para>
      </step>
    </directions>
    <notes>
      <note>
	<para>You may also use parsley in the place of the mint.</para>
